2013年6月，艾茲拉在[[格拉斯頓伯里當代表演藝術節|格拉斯頓伯里當代表演藝術節]]裡BBC的介紹舞台上演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVYY39fZfqk|title=George Ezra – Interview – DSCVR ONES TO WATCH 2014|publisher=[[Vevo|Vevo]]|accessdate=11 January 2014|archive-date=2019-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110063423/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVYY39fZfqk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年10月，他推出了他的出道EP《聽見雨聲嗎?》，[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]亦開始定期播放著他的歌曲《聽見雨聲嗎?》與《布達佩斯》。隨後艾茲拉陸續被選為[[音樂電視網|MTV]]「2014最佳新人」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/brand-new-for-2014/news/meet-mtvs-brand-new-for-2014-nominees|title=Meet MTV's Brand New For 2014 Nominees!|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=27 November 2013|accessdate=4 November 2014|archive-date=2014-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030101319/http://www.mtv.co.uk/brand-new-for-2014/news/meet-mtvs-brand-new-for-2014-nominees|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[VEVO|VEVO]]「2014值得關注新人」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVYY39fZfqk|title=George Ezra - Interview: DSCVR ONES TO WATCH 2014|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=10 December 2013|accessdate=4 November 2014|archive-date=2014-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217133317/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVYY39fZfqk&feature=c4-overview-vl&list=PL9tY0BWXOZFt7Ud0gCKMOktkOfpa6jZ7S|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[iTunes|iTunes]]「2014新人」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/itunes-unveils-its-artist-picks-for-2014/057134|title=iTunes unveils its artist picks for 2014|work=[[Music_Week|Music Week]]|date=20 December 2013|accessdate=4 November 2014|author=Pakinkis, Tom|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104124426/http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/itunes-unveils-its-artist-picks-for-2014/057134|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾茲拉亦入選[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]舉辦的「[[年度新聲|年度新聲]]」的評選活動，並最終成為第五名<ref>{{cite web |title=Soundcheck – Introducing: George Ezra |url=http://thisissoundcheck.co.uk/introducing-george-ezra/ |publisher=Soundcheck |accessdate=8 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221220921/http://thisissoundcheck.co.uk/introducing-george-ezra/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

單曲《布達佩斯》打進了意大利單曲榜第6名，並獲意大利音樂產業聯合會認證為白金唱片<ref>{{cite certification|region=Italy|type=single|artist=George Ezra|accessdate=7 April 2014|title=Budapest}}</ref>。艾茲拉也跟從歌手{{link-en|莉安拉·哈瓦斯|Lianne La Havas}}與{{link-en|湯姆·奧德爾|Tom Odell}}於他們的演唱會上作演出<ref>{{cite web|title=George Ezra: No 5 in the BBC Sound of 2014|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2014/jan/06/george-ezra-bbc-sound-of-2014-new-act|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|accessdate=5 April 2014|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095232/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2014/jan/06/george-ezra-bbc-sound-of-2014-new-act|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月，他推出了個人第2張EP《凱西歐》。《布達佩斯》則在6月於英國作單曲發行，同月發行了他的出道專輯《{{link-en|夢想啟航|Wanted on Voyage}}》並空降英國專輯榜第3名<ref>[http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/ed-sheeran-denies-5-seconds-of-summer-this-weeks-number-1-album-3145/ Ed Sheeran denies 5 Seconds Of Summer this week's Number 1 album] {{Wayback|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/ed-sheeran-denies-5-seconds-of-summer-this-weeks-number-1-album-3145/ |date=20141006103045 }}. [[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]].</ref>，並打進[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[比利時|比利時]]、[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]、[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]與[[瑞士|瑞士]]等地的專輯榜。同年10月5日，經過發行14周後，專輯升上英國專輯榜榜首位置。同年12月，專輯以678,156張銷量登上了英國全年專輯銷量榜第3名<ref name="UK top 40 2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-artist-albums-of-2014-3387/|title=The Official Top 40 Biggest Selling Artist Albums of 2014|last=Moss|first=Liv|date=1 January 2015|publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=1 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101030807/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-artist-albums-of-2014-3387/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月，專輯再次升上週榜榜首位置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/george-ezras-wanted-on-voyage-reclaims-official-albums-chart-number-1-3392/|title=George Ezra’s Wanted On Voyage reclaims Official Albums Chart Number 1|work=officialcharts.com|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109233336/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/george-ezras-wanted-on-voyage-reclaims-official-albums-chart-number-1-3392/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年8月10日，艾茲拉跟隨歌手[[羅伯特·普蘭特|羅伯特·普蘭特]]於格拉斯頓伯裡修道院作演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk/2014-glastonbury-abbey-extravaganza-in-pictures/|title=2014 Glastonbury Abbey Extravaganza in pictures - Glastonbury Festival|author=Pretty Good Digital|work=glastonburyfestivals.co.uk|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211022327/http://www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk/2014-glastonbury-abbey-extravaganza-in-pictures/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 音樂風格 ==
艾茲拉主要受[[卜·戴倫|卜·戴倫]]與[[伍迪·蓋瑟瑞|伍迪·蓋瑟瑞]]的音樂影響，他的男中低音被形容為帶[[藍調|藍調]]的感覺，《當留聲機響起》評論他為「他的年代以外的聲音」，以及「一個深情、乾癟的腔調，不禁令人覺得像一個正在[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]捕蝦艇上歸家的船長多於一個21歲的小伙子。<ref>{{cite web|title=REVIEW: GEORGE EZRA // DID YOU HEAR THE RAIN? EP|url=http://whenthegramophonerings.com/2013/11/05/review-george-ezra-hear-rain-ep/|publisher=When the Gramophone Rings|accessdate=11 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111142753/http://whenthegramophonerings.com/2013/11/05/review-george-ezra-hear-rain-ep/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」

艾茲拉小時候已經迷上卜·戴倫的音樂，這亦使他去尋找其他更早期美國民謠與藍調的歌手。他說：「出於好奇，我去尋找他曾經聽過誰的歌手。」、「這時我找到了{{link-en|利德·貝利|Lead Belly}}、伍迪·蓋瑟瑞與[[切斯特·阿瑟·伯内特|嚎叫野狼]]。」艾茲拉曾聽過貝利的唱片集，並嘗試模仿他的唱法，說：「唱片的背面寫著由於他的嗓音非常大，因此需要調低你的音響的音量。」、「我很喜歡用大嗓子唱歌這個想法，所以我嘗試一下，而我也能做到。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/09/14/george-ezra-budapest-on-the-verge/14706583/|title=On the Verge: George Ezra arrives by way of 'Budapest'|author=Brian Mansfield, Special for USA TODAY|date=14 September 2014|publisher=USA Today|accessdate=5 December 2014|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025162319/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/09/14/george-ezra-budapest-on-the-verge/14706583/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」

